name: Metal Fingers - Special Herbs - The Box Set vol.0-9 (vinyl)
description: This limited edition vinyl box set compiles the entire 10 volume ‘Special Herbs’ series, much of which has never before been available on wax, all in metallic silver jackets. In addition, the box includes an exclusive Doom poster, a download card for the entire ‘Special Herbs’ plus 10 additional Doom beats, and a bonus 7" with two more instrumentals from the metal-faced producer. Unlike 2006's 3CD mix, this collection contains all the beats in their full, original form, making it the definitive Doom instrumental anthology.
